’Щ@ddc2bcf94b052a2bcc41eb2954731ce1c371c253c95e7951935bb1899ef17a47ЩІTitle: title: Nushell 0.105.1
Path: Nushell 0.105.1
Content:
Today, we're releasing version 0.105.1 of Nu. This release adds a fix to make 
``cargo install nu``
 possible again.
’Щ@e05a48933ffd379d0889d37750379c5d94ca256920ec302cb3cb0ebeb984cbb7ЪОTitle: title: Nushell 0.105.1
Path: Where to get it
Content:
Nu 0.105.1 is available as 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/releases/tag/0.105.1] pre-built binaries
 or from 
[link: https://crates.io/crates/nu] crates.io
. If you have Rust installed you can install it using 
``cargo install nu``
.
As part of this release, we also publish a set of optional 
[link: https://www.nushell.sh/book/plugins.html] plugins
 you can install and use with Nushell.
